Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.99,0:00:57.07,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz30.04\pos(232,446)}分镜总监
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.99,0:00:57.07,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz30.04\pos(487.502,730)}编剧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.99,0:00:59.53,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1096,976.667)}翻译{\fnArial}: 1440kHz
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.28,0:00:59.53,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz30.63\pos(396.547,399.334)}技术总监
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.28,0:00:59.53,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz30.63\pos(526.728,653.334)}动画总监
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.74,0:01:02.20,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz31.17\pos(421.346,538.667)}制片指导
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.74,0:01:02.20,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1034.667,976.667)}本字幕仅限学习交流\N严禁用于商业用途
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.20,0:01:03.41,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1006,776)}裤头村
Dialogue: 1,0:01:06.80,0:01:07.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快逃命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.80,0:01:07.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Run for it, man
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.85,0:01:21.81,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(492,704)}海之霸
Dialogue: 1,0:01:25.28,0:01:27.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好啊  午餐高峰客流
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.28,0:01:27.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good, the lunch rush
Dialogue: 1,0:01:27.10,0:01:31.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,既然海霸机让你们落入了我的魔掌
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.10,0:01:31.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now that my Chumbot has dropped you into my clutches
Dialogue: 1,0:01:31.04,0:01:34.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们就必须在海之霸用餐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.04,0:01:34.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you'll be forced to eat at the Chum Bucket
Dialogue: 1,0:01:35.40,0:01:36.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.40,0:01:36.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:36.36,0:01:39.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以你是想卖快餐才绑架我们的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.36,0:01:39.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you mean you kidnapped us just to sell us your fast food?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:39.37,0:01:42.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,得了吧  这可是标准营销技巧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.37,0:01:42.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, it's a standard marketing technique
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.41,0:01:44.41,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(512,248)}出口
Dialogue: 1,0:01:43.42,0:01:44.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你这小呆子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.42,0:01:44.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You little twerp
Dialogue: 1,0:01:46.01,0:01:47.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他说得对
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.01,0:01:47.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's right, you know
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.54,0:01:48.75,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(466,184)}厨房
Dialogue: 1,0:01:47.92,0:01:48.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,凯伦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.92,0:01:48.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Karen
Dialogue: 1,0:01:49.07,0:01:51.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你觉得我是呆子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.07,0:01:51.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You think I'm a twerp?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:51.50,0:01:52.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.50,0:01:52.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, yes
Dialogue: 1,0:01:52.30,0:01:54.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但我指的是绑架的事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.30,0:01:54.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but I was referring to the kidnapping
Dialogue: 1,0:01:54.38,0:01:57.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在你眼中  我干什么都是错的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.38,0:01:57.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Everything I do is always wrong in your eyes
Dialogue: 1,0:01:57.55,0:02:00.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,也许是因为你向来都是错的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.55,0:02:00.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's because you are always wrong
Dialogue: 1,0:02:00.39,0:02:01.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.39,0:02:01.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fine--
Dialogue: 1,0:02:01.30,0:02:03.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我都错  你都对
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.30,0:02:03.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm wrong, you're right
Dialogue: 1,0:02:03.14,0:02:03.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你说的  不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.14,0:02:03.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You said it, not me
Dialogue: 1,0:02:03.93,0:02:06.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我为什么要装上那个唠叨软件
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.93,0:02:06.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why did I ever install that nagging software?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:06.30,0:02:07.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,唠叨软件
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.30,0:02:07.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nagging software?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:07.24,0:02:08.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我都听到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.24,0:02:08.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I heard that
Dialogue: 1,0:02:08.17,0:02:09.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,回来帮我屏幕清灰
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.17,0:02:09.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come back here and dust my screen
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.02,0:02:12.23,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(408,422)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:02:10.88,0:02:12.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,钱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.88,0:02:12.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, money
Dialogue: 1,0:02:12.23,0:02:14.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你总是能出手挺我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.23,0:02:14.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you're always there for me
Dialogue: 1,0:02:15.61,0:02:16.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好啊  尤金
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.61,0:02:16.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello, Eugene
Dialogue: 1,0:02:16.82,0:02:17.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老妈
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.82,0:02:17.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mother
Dialogue: 1,0:02:18.30,0:02:19.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么风把你吹来的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.30,0:02:19.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What brings you by today?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:19.73,0:02:20.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我只想见见
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.73,0:02:20.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I just wanted to see
Dialogue: 1,0:02:20.78,0:02:22.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的宝贝儿子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.78,0:02:22.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,me favorite son
Dialogue: 1,0:02:23.17,0:02:25.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你想要多少钱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.17,0:02:25.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How much of my money do you want?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:25.30,0:02:28.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我今天看到了镇上最漂亮的帽子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.30,0:02:28.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I did see the prettiest hat in town today
Dialogue: 1,0:02:29.77,0:02:31.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都这么晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.77,0:02:31.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look at the time
Dialogue: 1,0:02:31.13,0:02:32.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉  有急事先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.13,0:02:32.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So sorry to have to rush off
Dialogue: 1,0:02:32.56,0:02:33.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.56,0:02:33.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bye, bye
Dialogue: 1,0:02:34.59,0:02:35.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真是好险啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.59,0:02:35.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That was a close one
Dialogue: 1,0:02:37.85,0:02:41.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我干嘛要买那个电脑老婆
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.85,0:02:41.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why did I ever buy that computer wife?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:41.57,0:02:43.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我需要真正的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.57,0:02:43.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I need a real woman--
Dialogue: 1,0:02:43.57,0:02:46.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不是外表冷漠又强硬的机器女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.57,0:02:46.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,not a girl in a cold, hard shell
Dialogue: 1,0:02:51.40,0:02:52.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好美啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.40,0:02:52.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Such beauty
Dialogue: 1,0:02:53.82,0:02:55.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,她就是个天使
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.82,0:02:55.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,She's an angel
Dialogue: 1,0:02:55.18,0:02:56.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还没电线
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.18,0:02:56.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and no wires
Dialogue: 1,0:02:56.60,0:02:58.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,从来没有过这种感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.60,0:02:58.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've never felt like this before
Dialogue: 1,0:02:59.25,0:03:00.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我连她名字都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.25,0:03:00.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't even know her name
Dialogue: 1,0:03:00.90,0:03:03.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,她却偷走了我的心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.90,0:03:03.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and yet she's stolen my heart
Dialogue: 1,0:03:03.77,0:03:04.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,痞老板
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.77,0:03:04.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Plankton
Dialogue: 1,0:03:04.83,0:03:07.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你又爱上了个另一个女人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.83,0:03:07.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You've fallen in love with another woman?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:07.42,0:03:08.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我可是你老婆
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.42,0:03:08.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm your wife
Dialogue: 1,0:03:08.77,0:03:10.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你就是个WIFE
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.77,0:03:10.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're a W.I.F.E.
Dialogue: 1,0:03:11.43,0:03:14.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,线路整合女性化脑电图仪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.43,0:03:14.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,wired integrated female electroencephalograph
Dialogue: 1,0:03:15.47,0:03:18.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你老用那套话术唬我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.47,0:03:18.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You always pull that one out
Dialogue: 1,0:03:18.15,0:03:19.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你才不是真正的老婆
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.15,0:03:19.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"You're not a real wife
Dialogue: 1,0:03:19.72,0:03:21.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你就只是台电脑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.72,0:03:21.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're just a computer"
Dialogue: 1,0:03:22.33,0:03:24.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你怎么连个关闭按钮都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.33,0:03:24.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why don't you have an "off" switch?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.85,0:03:25.76,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(442,386)}关
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.85,0:03:25.76,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(442,648)}开
Dialogue: 1,0:03:26.43,0:03:30.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,痞老板  你休想
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.43,0:03:30.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Plankton, don't you dare
Dialogue: 1,0:03:30.44,0:03:34.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来追求那只心爱的生物吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.44,0:03:34.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And now to woo that beloved creature
Dialogue: 1,0:03:41.58,0:03:43.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,玫瑰是红的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.58,0:03:43.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Roses are red
Dialogue: 1,0:03:43.67,0:03:45.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,紫罗兰是蓝的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.67,0:03:45.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Violets are blue
Dialogue: 1,0:03:45.52,0:03:49.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,统治世界完全比不上你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.52,0:03:49.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,World domination has nothing on you
Dialogue: 1,0:03:51.42,0:03:53.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,估计她不是很喜欢诗歌
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.42,0:03:53.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I guess she's not a poetry fan
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.51,0:04:01.51,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(388,862)}我爱你
Dialogue: 1,0:04:06.72,0:04:08.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,诗歌  情书
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.72,0:04:08.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Poetry, love notes--
Dialogue: 1,0:04:08.42,0:04:09.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,全都没用
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.42,0:04:09.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,nothing's working
Dialogue: 1,0:04:09.92,0:04:11.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可能得试试私人点的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.92,0:04:11.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Maybe something personal
Dialogue: 1,0:04:20.55,0:04:22.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我真有那么漂亮吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.55,0:04:22.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Am I really that pretty?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:23.52,0:04:24.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.52,0:04:24.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:04:24.69,0:04:26.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我太顺利了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.69,0:04:26.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I am smooth
Dialogue: 1,0:04:27.87,0:04:30.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,打电话叫她来共进晚餐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.87,0:04:30.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just dial the number and ask her to dinner
Dialogue: 1,0:04:30.58,0:04:33.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,加油  你能行的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.58,0:04:33.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, you can do this
Dialogue: 1,0:04:39.55,0:04:40.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.55,0:04:40.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:42.84,0:04:43.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要挂了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.84,0:04:43.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm hanging up
Dialogue: 1,0:04:43.95,0:04:44.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别挂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.95,0:04:44.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait
Dialogue: 1,0:04:44.55,0:04:46.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是暗恋你的那位
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.55,0:04:46.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's your secret admirer
Dialogue: 1,0:04:47.45,0:04:49.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你就是那个巨型机器人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.45,0:04:49.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're that giant robot?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:50.64,0:04:51.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.64,0:04:51.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:04:51.45,0:04:52.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,机器人的程序是我做的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.45,0:04:52.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I program the robot
Dialogue: 1,0:04:52.75,0:04:54.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,喜不喜欢我送你的礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.75,0:04:54.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Did you enjoy the gift I sent you?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:55.12,0:04:56.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你怎么知道我想要帽子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.12,0:04:56.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How did you know I wanted a hat?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:57.20,0:04:59.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你是不是在监视我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.20,0:04:59.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Have you been spying on me?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:59.70,0:05:00.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.70,0:05:00.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It was
Dialogue: 1,0:05:00.85,0:05:02.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只是正好猜中而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.85,0:05:02.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,just a lucky guess
Dialogue: 1,0:05:02.30,0:05:06.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我已经暗恋你很久了  我的小天使
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.30,0:05:06.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've admired you from afar for too long, my angel
Dialogue: 1,0:05:06.23,0:05:08.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一定要来见个面
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.23,0:05:08.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We must meet face-to-face
Dialogue: 1,0:05:08.15,0:05:11.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要不今晚八点到蟹堡王见面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.15,0:05:11.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, how about the Krusty Krab tonight at 8:00?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:11.58,0:05:13.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一听就不错
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.58,0:05:13.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sounds wonderful
Dialogue: 1,0:05:13.37,0:05:16.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,到时候戴着红色康乃馨的高个就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.37,0:05:16.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll be the tall fellow wearing a red carnation
Dialogue: 1,0:05:16.36,0:05:18.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今晚见
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.36,0:05:18.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Until tonight
Dialogue: 1,0:05:18.37,0:05:19.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的宝贝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.37,0:05:19.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,my dear
Dialogue: 1,0:05:24.45,0:05:25.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快点  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.45,0:05:25.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Quick, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:05:25.22,0:05:26.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,吞我钱包
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.22,0:05:26.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,swallow me wallet
Dialogue: 1,0:05:26.01,0:05:26.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.01,0:05:26.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 1,0:05:28.25,0:05:29.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉  老妈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.25,0:05:29.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Mommy
Dialogue: 1,0:05:29.14,0:05:30.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没办法让你借钱了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.14,0:05:30.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't lend you any money
Dialogue: 1,0:05:30.73,0:05:33.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝不小心把我钱包给吞了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.73,0:05:33.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob accidentally swallowed me wallet
Dialogue: 1,0:05:34.27,0:05:37.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老妈  你没我资助就买了顶帽子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.27,0:05:36.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mommy, you got yourself a hat
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.39,0:05:37.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,without me financial assistance
Dialogue: 1,0:05:37.65,0:05:39.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,很棒吧  尤金
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.65,0:05:39.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Isn't it nice, Eugene?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:39.50,0:05:41.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,正好是我想要的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.50,0:05:41.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's just the one I wanted
Dialogue: 1,0:05:41.11,0:05:44.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可是老妈  你不应该乱花我遗产
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.11,0:05:44.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But, Mommy, you shouldn't be spending my inheritance
Dialogue: 1,0:05:44.35,0:05:46.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是说  既然你说想要顶帽子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.35,0:05:46.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I mean, since you told me you wanted a hat
Dialogue: 1,0:05:46.49,0:05:48.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就去挖了一顶出来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.49,0:05:48.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I went out and dug one up
Dialogue: 1,0:05:48.20,0:05:50.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你上哪找的这种旧货
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.20,0:05:50.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where did you get this old thing?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:50.66,0:05:52.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,她看着可真安详
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.66,0:05:52.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,She looks so peaceful
Dialogue: 1,0:05:52.65,0:05:55.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是啊  可她先前不是还戴着顶帽子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.65,0:05:55.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but wasn't she wearing a hat?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:56.25,0:05:59.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可以把这玩意扔回垃圾堆了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.25,0:05:59.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You can take this back to the trash heap
Dialogue: 1,0:05:59.10,0:06:00.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好的  老妈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.10,0:06:00.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, Mommy
Dialogue: 1,0:06:00.25,0:06:02.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  替我去还帽子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.25,0:06:02.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward, I need you to make a return for me
Dialogue: 1,0:06:02.71,0:06:06.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,多谢你关心我的财务状况
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.71,0:06:06.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank ye for your concern about me finances
Dialogue: 1,0:06:06.12,0:06:08.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但这顶帽子是我新男友给我买的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.12,0:06:08.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but me new boyfriend bought me this hat
Dialogue: 1,0:06:08.22,0:06:08.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,男朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.22,0:06:08.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Boyfriend?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:08.97,0:06:10.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有人愿意花钱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.97,0:06:10.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Someone to spend money
Dialogue: 1,0:06:10.10,0:06:11.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是说花时间陪你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.10,0:06:11.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I mean, "time" with you?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:11.55,0:06:13.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太美妙了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.55,0:06:13.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's wonderful
Dialogue: 1,0:06:13.10,0:06:13.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.10,0:06:13.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who is he?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:13.77,0:06:14.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他叫什么名字
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.77,0:06:14.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's his name?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:14.70,0:06:15.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.70,0:06:15.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't know
Dialogue: 1,0:06:15.97,0:06:17.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今晚就要在这里跟他见面
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.97,0:06:17.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm meeting him here tonight
Dialogue: 1,0:06:17.97,0:06:18.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.97,0:06:18.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wonderful
Dialogue: 1,0:06:18.94,0:06:19.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我会营业到很晚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.94,0:06:19.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll stay open late
Dialogue: 1,0:06:19.94,0:06:21.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让你能享用美好又浪漫的晚餐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.94,0:06:21.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,so ye can have a nice, romantic dinner
Dialogue: 1,0:06:21.97,0:06:24.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,去吧  打扮得美美的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.97,0:06:24.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Run along, make yourself pretty
Dialogue: 1,0:06:24.50,0:06:26.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  你今晚得加班
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.50,0:06:26.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, you're working late tonight
Dialogue: 1,0:06:26.41,0:06:27.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不付加班费
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.41,0:06:27.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No overtime
Dialogue: 1,0:06:32.40,0:06:35.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我今晚预定了两个人的位子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.40,0:06:35.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've reservations for two tonight
Dialogue: 1,0:06:35.62,0:06:37.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这边请  先生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.62,0:06:37.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Right this way, sir
Dialogue: 1,0:06:40.17,0:06:41.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.17,0:06:41.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Excuse me
Dialogue: 1,0:06:41.61,0:06:43.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我够不到银餐具
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.61,0:06:43.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't reach my silverware
Dialogue: 1,0:06:43.29,0:06:44.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,万分抱歉  先生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.29,0:06:44.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Terribly sorry, sir
Dialogue: 1,0:06:49.47,0:06:50.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.47,0:06:50.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Will there be anything else?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:51.05,0:06:52.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我领带打直了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.05,0:06:52.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Is my tie on straight?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:52.43,0:06:54.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可漂亮了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.43,0:06:54.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You look fabulous
Dialogue: 1,0:06:56.43,0:06:59.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拜访您的先生已经等候多时
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.43,0:06:59.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Your gentleman caller awaits
Dialogue: 1,0:07:00.75,0:07:02.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好  亲爱的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.75,0:07:02.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello, my dear
Dialogue: 1,0:07:02.35,0:07:06.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不得不说  你今晚美丽动人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.35,0:07:06.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I must say you look ravishing tonight
Dialogue: 1,0:07:06.70,0:07:09.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天啊  你个子虽然小
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.70,0:07:09.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh my, you're a tiny thing
Dialogue: 1,0:07:09.47,0:07:11.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但也太可爱了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.47,0:07:11.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but awfully cute
Dialogue: 1,0:07:11.03,0:07:12.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,介绍一下你自己吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.03,0:07:12.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Tell me about yourself
Dialogue: 1,0:07:12.28,0:07:15.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是搞餐饮业的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.28,0:07:15.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm in the food service business
Dialogue: 1,0:07:15.52,0:07:17.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,算是个餐厅老板吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.52,0:07:17.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm a bit of a restaurateur
Dialogue: 1,0:07:17.52,0:07:19.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是海之霸的创立者兼老板
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.52,0:07:19.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm the founder and owner of the Chum Bucket
Dialogue: 1,0:07:19.75,0:07:20.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,从来没听说过
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.75,0:07:20.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Never heard of it
Dialogue: 1,0:07:21.66,0:07:23.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就在街对面
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.66,0:07:23.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's across the street
Dialogue: 1,0:07:23.00,0:07:24.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没印象
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.00,0:07:24.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Doesn't ring a bell
Dialogue: 1,0:07:24.09,0:07:26.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就印在电话簿背面
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.09,0:07:26.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's on the back of the phone book
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.25,0:07:29.05,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(402,510)}海之霸\N不吃就去死
Dialogue: 1,0:07:26.17,0:07:28.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真是的  我花了不少广告费呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.17,0:07:28.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, I paid a lot of money for that ad
Dialogue: 1,0:07:29.28,0:07:30.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没关系  没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.28,0:07:30.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Never mind, never mind
Dialogue: 1,0:07:31.16,0:07:32.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我想听听你的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.16,0:07:32.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'd like to hear about you
Dialogue: 1,0:07:32.68,0:07:33.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.68,0:07:33.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well
Dialogue: 1,0:07:34.14,0:07:34.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老痞子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.14,0:07:34.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Plankton
Dialogue: 1,0:07:34.76,0:07:35.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老螃蟹
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.76,0:07:35.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:07:36.01,0:07:36.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,尤金
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.01,0:07:36.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Eugene
Dialogue: 1,0:07:36.92,0:07:37.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老妈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.92,0:07:37.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mommy?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:37.67,0:07:38.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老妈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.67,0:07:38.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Mommy"?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:38.72,0:07:39.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.72,0:07:39.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:07:39.92,0:07:41.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.92,0:07:41.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:07:41.72,0:07:44.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这秀色可餐的生物是你妈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.72,0:07:44.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This delectable creature is your mother?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:44.69,0:07:48.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这阴险狡诈的死骗子是你对象
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.69,0:07:48.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This no-good conniving chiseler is your date?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:48.17,0:07:50.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这位帅哥海绵是你们服务生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.17,0:07:50.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And this devilishly handsome sponge is your waiter
Dialogue: 1,0:07:50.53,0:07:51.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.53,0:07:51.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:07:51.82,0:07:55.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不知道你在耍什么阴谋诡计  痞老板
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.82,0:07:52.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't know what sort of
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.91,0:07:55.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,skullduggery you're up to, Plankton
Dialogue: 1,0:07:55.03,0:07:57.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我也懒得等着去揭穿
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.03,0:07:57.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and I'm not waiting to find out
Dialogue: 1,0:07:57.70,0:08:01.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,尤金  马上把我男朋友放下来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.70,0:08:01.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Eugene, you put me boyfriend down this instant
Dialogue: 1,0:08:01.66,0:08:02.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,男朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.66,0:08:02.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Boyfriend?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:02.96,0:08:03.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可是老妈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.96,0:08:03.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But, Mommy
Dialogue: 1,0:08:03.92,0:08:05.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,听见她的话了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.92,0:08:05.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You heard the lady
Dialogue: 1,0:08:05.56,0:08:06.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放我下来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.56,0:08:06.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let me go
Dialogue: 1,0:08:08.40,0:08:09.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这还差不多
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.40,0:08:09.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's more like it
Dialogue: 1,0:08:09.89,0:08:11.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来吧  痞老板
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.89,0:08:11.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come, Plankton
Dialogue: 1,0:08:11.17,0:08:14.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真抱歉儿子非要搞砸我们的浪漫夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.17,0:08:14.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry me son had to spoil our romantic evening
Dialogue: 1,0:08:15.62,0:08:16.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老妈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.62,0:08:16.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mommy?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:21.56,0:08:22.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.56,0:08:22.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You
Dialogue: 1,0:08:22.56,0:08:23.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,尤金
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.56,0:08:23.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Eugene
Dialogue: 1,0:08:23.32,0:08:25.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我来警告你  痞老板
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.32,0:08:25.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I came to warn you, Plankton
Dialogue: 1,0:08:25.38,0:08:26.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,离我妈远点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.38,0:08:26.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stay away from me mother
Dialogue: 1,0:08:26.77,0:08:28.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我知道你有什么打算
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.77,0:08:28.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know what you're really up to
Dialogue: 1,0:08:28.52,0:08:30.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是认真的  尤金
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.52,0:08:30.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm serious, Eugene
Dialogue: 1,0:08:30.16,0:08:31.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我已经洗心革面了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.16,0:08:31.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've changed my ways
Dialogue: 1,0:08:31.87,0:08:35.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都是美女的爱感化了我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.87,0:08:35.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And all it took was the love of a beautiful woman
Dialogue: 1,0:08:35.32,0:08:37.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你就只爱小偷小摸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.32,0:08:37.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All you love is thieving and conniving
Dialogue: 1,0:08:37.99,0:08:40.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,休想借我妈偷到秘方
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.99,0:08:40.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, stop trying to get the formula out of me mother
Dialogue: 1,0:08:40.91,0:08:43.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你胡说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.91,0:08:43.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:43.21,0:08:45.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我说的就是蟹黄堡的秘密配方
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.21,0:08:45.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm talking about the Krabby Patty formula
Dialogue: 1,0:08:45.58,0:08:48.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你妈知道蟹黄堡的秘密配方吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.58,0:08:48.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Your mother knows the Krabby Patty formula?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:48.88,0:08:51.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,少给我装傻
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.88,0:08:51.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't play stupid with me
Dialogue: 1,0:08:51.44,0:08:52.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,她当然知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.44,0:08:52.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Of course she does
Dialogue: 1,0:08:52.95,0:08:54.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那可是祖传秘方
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.95,0:08:54.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's an old Krabs family recipe
Dialogue: 1,0:08:54.80,0:08:56.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你又不是我家里人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.80,0:08:56.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And you're not family
Dialogue: 1,0:08:57.12,0:08:59.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最后再警告你一次
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.12,0:08:59.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm telling you for the last time
Dialogue: 1,0:08:59.22,0:09:01.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,离我妈远点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.22,0:09:01.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,stay away from me mother
Dialogue: 1,0:09:02.50,0:09:04.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不是你家里人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.50,0:09:04.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not family, eh?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:04.45,0:09:06.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这我能解决
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.45,0:09:06.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I can fix that
Dialogue: 1,0:09:08.02,0:09:09.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,尤金
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.02,0:09:09.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Eugene
Dialogue: 1,0:09:09.05,0:09:09.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老妈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.05,0:09:09.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mommy
Dialogue: 1,0:09:09.65,0:09:12.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,干涉我私生活的事  我怎么跟你说的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.65,0:09:12.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What did I tell ye about interfering in me life?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:12.42,0:09:14.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老妈  你就看不出来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.42,0:09:14.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mommy, can't you see?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:14.21,0:09:17.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他这是想从你身上套取蟹黄堡秘方
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.21,0:09:16.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's trying to seduce the Krabby Patty formula
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.53,0:09:17.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,right from under you
Dialogue: 1,0:09:17.41,0:09:19.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,提醒你一句  尤金
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.41,0:09:19.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,For your information, Eugene
Dialogue: 1,0:09:19.82,0:09:22.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他从来就没有问过我秘方
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.82,0:09:22.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,he hasn't asked me once about the formula
Dialogue: 1,0:09:22.23,0:09:24.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,多半还不清楚我知道秘方
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.23,0:09:24.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I doubt that he even knows that I know it
Dialogue: 1,0:09:25.62,0:09:25.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.62,0:09:25.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:09:25.95,0:09:27.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这可真奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.95,0:09:27.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,funny thing about that
Dialogue: 1,0:09:27.05,0:09:30.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我禁止你干涉我的私生活
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.05,0:09:30.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I forbid ye to interfere in me private business
Dialogue: 1,0:09:30.72,0:09:32.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,回你办公室去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.72,0:09:32.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Go to your office
Dialogue: 1,0:09:32.42,0:09:33.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,马上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.42,0:09:33.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now
Dialogue: 1,0:09:33.27,0:09:34.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  老妈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.27,0:09:34.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, Mommy
Dialogue: 1,0:09:36.84,0:09:38.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快给天堂打个电话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.84,0:09:38.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Somebody call heaven
Dialogue: 1,0:09:38.24,0:09:40.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好像有位天使失踪了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.24,0:09:40.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,because I think an angel's gone missing
Dialogue: 1,0:09:40.70,0:09:42.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢尔顿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.70,0:09:42.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, Sheldon
Dialogue: 1,0:09:42.32,0:09:44.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹太太啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.32,0:09:44.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, Mrs. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:09:44.77,0:09:46.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可真是的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.77,0:09:46.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, brother
Dialogue: 1,0:09:46.65,0:09:49.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家请注意
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.65,0:09:49.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Attention, attention, everyone
Dialogue: 1,0:09:49.35,0:09:51.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我宣布个事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.35,0:09:51.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'd like to make an announcement
Dialogue: 1,0:09:51.56,0:09:54.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹太太  在全蟹堡王见证之下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.56,0:09:54.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mrs. Krabs, in full view of this restaurant
Dialogue: 1,0:09:54.97,0:09:58.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我请求与你结为婚姻
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.97,0:09:58.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I ask you for your hand in holy matrimony
Dialogue: 1,0:10:00.69,0:10:02.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你愿意嫁给我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.69,0:10:02.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Would you marry me?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:04.90,0:10:05.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我得了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.90,0:10:05.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's it
Dialogue: 1,0:10:05.90,0:10:08.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不能再胆小幼稚地躲在我房间里了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.90,0:10:08.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No more hiding in my room like a scared little kid
Dialogue: 1,0:10:08.37,0:10:09.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,该来表现成熟点了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.37,0:10:09.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's time to act like a man
Dialogue: 1,0:10:13.92,0:10:15.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,求你别嫁给他  老妈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.92,0:10:15.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Please don't marry him, Mommy
Dialogue: 1,0:10:15.17,0:10:16.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别嫁给这个大坏蛋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.17,0:10:16.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't marry this bad, bad man
Dialogue: 1,0:10:16.69,0:10:19.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你可千万别啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.69,0:10:19.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't want you to
Dialogue: 1,0:10:19.24,0:10:20.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来不及了  小蟹
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.24,0:10:20.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Too late, Krabsy
Dialogue: 1,0:10:20.80,0:10:22.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们就快结婚了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.80,0:10:22.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're going to be married
Dialogue: 1,0:10:22.27,0:10:25.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你马上就是我的新儿子了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.27,0:10:25.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And you're going to be my new son
Dialogue: 1,0:10:30.10,0:10:31.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么了  小甜甜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.10,0:10:31.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's this, honey bunch?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:31.69,0:10:33.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你的赠礼让我受宠若惊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.69,0:10:33.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I am flattered by your offer
Dialogue: 1,0:10:33.92,0:10:35.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.92,0:10:35.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Really I am
Dialogue: 1,0:10:35.17,0:10:38.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但我还没准备好做出那样的承诺
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.17,0:10:38.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But I'm just not ready for that kind of commitment
Dialogue: 1,0:10:41.24,0:10:42.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.24,0:10:42.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:43.12,0:10:44.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是不是还有其他对象
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.12,0:10:44.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's somebody else, isn't there?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:47.76,0:10:48.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.76,0:10:48.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I
Dialogue: 1,0:10:48.57,0:10:49.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.57,0:10:49.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I
Dialogue: 1,0:10:49.90,0:10:52.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太难受了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.90,0:10:52.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is very uncomfortable
Dialogue: 1,0:10:52.78,0:10:54.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我还是在车上等吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.78,0:10:54.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll just wait in the car
Dialogue: 1,0:10:56.17,0:10:58.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我真不敢相信
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.17,0:10:58.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't believe this
Dialogue: 1,0:10:58.32,0:10:59.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你骗了我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.32,0:10:59.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You led me on
Dialogue: 1,0:10:59.50,0:11:00.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没事  痞老板
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.50,0:11:00.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, now, Plankton
Dialogue: 1,0:11:00.78,0:11:01.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,事情不是你想的那样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.78,0:11:01.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,it's not what ye think
Dialogue: 1,0:11:01.97,0:11:04.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不想再听你的谎言了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.97,0:11:04.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't want to hear your lies
Dialogue: 1,0:11:04.30,0:11:06.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你这么骗我  那就欠我一个人情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.30,0:11:06.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You owe me for leading me on like this
Dialogue: 1,0:11:07.35,0:11:09.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹黄堡秘方给我  就一笔勾销
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.35,0:11:09.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Give me the Krabby Patty formula, and we'll call it even
Dialogue: 1,0:11:09.81,0:11:11.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,秘方
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.81,0:11:11.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The formula?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:11.89,0:11:14.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以这才是你的打算吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.89,0:11:14.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Is that what this whole thing was about?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:14.02,0:11:16.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对  不完全是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.02,0:11:16.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, no, not really
Dialogue: 1,0:11:16.47,0:11:18.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,至少一开始不是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.47,0:11:18.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I mean, not at first
Dialogue: 1,0:11:18.99,0:11:20.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.99,0:11:20.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I mean, uh
Dialogue: 1,0:11:20.85,0:11:21.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小甜甜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.85,0:11:21.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Honey bunch?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:25.49,0:11:26.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.49,0:11:26.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, well
Dialogue: 1,0:11:26.41,0:11:28.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,曾经深爱过  现在失去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.41,0:11:28.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,'tis better to have loved and lost
Dialogue: 1,0:11:28.24,0:11:30.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,总比从没爱过好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.24,0:11:30.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,than never to have loved at all
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.66,0:11:32.29,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(402,654)}开
Dialogue: 1,0:11:33.37,0:11:34.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,已启动
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.37,0:11:34.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Working
Dialogue: 1,0:11:34.64,0:11:37.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你总算决定爬回来找我了是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.64,0:11:37.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So you've decided to come crawling back to me, huh?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:37.96,0:11:39.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.96,0:11:39.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:40.08,0:11:41.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没什么  老婆
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.08,0:11:41.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nothing, dear
Dialogue: 1,0:11:44.28,0:11:48.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就知道你会那么说  小甜甜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.28,0:11:48.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's what I thought you said, honey bunch
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.35,0:11:55.61,起司 一般标题,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\fsp50\c&H00FFC1&\fs150\fsp30}美人鱼战士\N{\fs30} \N{\fs150}和企鹅男孩6\N{\fs30} \N{\fs150}大电影
