Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.45,0:12:03.24,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz29.08\pos(949.736,362)}配音  美人鱼战士
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.45,0:12:03.24,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz29.08\pos(1133.736,654)}配音  企鹅男孩
Dialogue: 1,0:12:06.49,0:12:08.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是美人鱼战士
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.49,0:12:08.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's Mermaidman
Dialogue: 1,0:12:08.17,0:12:09.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,深海的救星
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.17,0:12:09.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Savior of the deep
Dialogue: 1,0:12:10.10,0:12:12.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,与他的年轻得力助手  企鹅男孩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.10,0:12:12.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And his young, fit servant, Barnacleboy
Dialogue: 1,0:12:13.79,0:12:17.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,美人鱼战士和企鹅男孩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.79,0:12:17.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mermaidman and Barnacleboy
Dialogue: 1,0:12:17.04,0:12:18.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,合为一体
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.04,0:12:18.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,unite
Dialogue: 1,0:12:21.78,0:12:25.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海草怪  这里明令禁止停船
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.78,0:12:25.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Kelp-Thing, this is a posted no-parking zone
Dialogue: 1,0:12:26.58,0:12:29.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但我非要干这行不可
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.58,0:12:29.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But I must do what I do
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.90,0:12:36.06,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(832,824)}拖离
Dialogue: 1,0:12:36.06,0:12:43.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,坏蛋早六到晚十二禁止在这停船
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.06,0:12:38.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Evil can't park here
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.69,0:12:43.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,between the hours of 6:00 a.m. and 12:00 p.m.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.36,0:12:45.24,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(734,902)}本集完
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.70,0:12:46.32,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(938,310)}美人鱼战士和企鹅男孩\N粉丝俱乐部
Dialogue: 1,0:12:48.45,0:12:49.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,美人鱼战士和企鹅男孩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.45,0:12:49.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mermaidman and Barnacleboy
Dialogue: 1,0:12:49.79,0:12:50.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,粉丝俱乐部成员
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.79,0:12:50.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fan Club members
Dialogue: 1,0:12:50.71,0:12:51.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,合为一体
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.71,0:12:51.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,unite
Dialogue: 1,0:12:51.66,0:12:52.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,合为一体
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.66,0:12:52.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Unite
Dialogue: 1,0:12:52.79,0:12:54.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在是第二项要务
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.79,0:12:54.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And now, the second order of business
Dialogue: 1,0:12:54.87,0:12:57.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,德瑞皮兄弟制片厂目前正在拍摄
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.87,0:12:57.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Drippy Brothers Studios is currently in production
Dialogue: 1,0:12:57.48,0:13:00.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,美人鱼战士和企鹅男孩大电影
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.48,0:13:00.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,on the Mermaidman and Barnacleboy movie
Dialogue: 1,0:13:03.06,0:13:04.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天啊  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.06,0:13:04.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, boy, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:13:04.55,0:13:06.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我等不及要看我们最爱的英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.55,0:13:06.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can hardly wait to see our favorite heroes
Dialogue: 1,0:13:06.55,0:13:08.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,登上大银幕了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.55,0:13:08.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,on the big screen
Dialogue: 1,0:13:09.05,0:13:13.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,第三项要务  特别惊喜嘉宾
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.05,0:13:13.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Third order of business, the special surprise guest
Dialogue: 1,0:13:14.52,0:13:16.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,美人鱼战士大电影的主演明星
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.52,0:13:16.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The stars of the Mermaidman movie
Dialogue: 1,0:13:16.67,0:13:18.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今晚到场了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.67,0:13:18.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,are here tonight
Dialogue: 1,0:13:20.45,0:13:23.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在他们从片场过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.45,0:13:23.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Directly from the set, here they are
Dialogue: 1,0:13:23.55,0:13:24.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小英雄们好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.55,0:13:24.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello, little heroes
Dialogue: 1,0:13:25.65,0:13:28.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们不是美人鱼战士和企鹅男孩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.65,0:13:28.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're not Mermaidman and Barnacleboy
Dialogue: 1,0:13:28.20,0:13:29.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们是冒牌货
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.20,0:13:29.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're fakes
Dialogue: 1,0:13:29.53,0:13:30.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,当然假了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.53,0:13:30.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, of course we are--
Dialogue: 1,0:13:30.70,0:13:31.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们可是演员
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.70,0:13:31.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,we're actors
Dialogue: 1,0:13:31.75,0:13:32.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,演员
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.75,0:13:32.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Actors?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:32.79,0:13:35.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拍美人鱼战士大电影怎么可以
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.79,0:13:35.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How can you make a Mermaidman movie
Dialogue: 1,0:13:35.00,0:13:37.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不找真正的美人鱼战士和企鹅男孩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.00,0:13:37.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,without the real Mermaidman and Barnacleboy?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:37.46,0:13:39.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小子听好  这可是动作大片
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.46,0:13:39.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Listen, kid, this is an action movie
Dialogue: 1,0:13:39.46,0:13:42.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们的过气英雄太老了  没法打斗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.46,0:13:42.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Your has-been heroes are too old for action
Dialogue: 1,0:13:42.33,0:13:44.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,美人鱼战士永垂不朽
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.33,0:13:44.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mermaidman is timeless
Dialogue: 1,0:13:44.01,0:13:44.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.01,0:13:44.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:13:45.26,0:13:47.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我站在这里为大家说出心声
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.26,0:13:47.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I think I speak for everyone here
Dialogue: 1,0:13:47.12,0:13:48.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我认为大家绝对不会支持
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.12,0:13:48.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,when I say we won't stand
Dialogue: 1,0:13:48.68,0:13:50.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那两个冒牌货
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.68,0:13:50.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,for these two phony baloneys
Dialogue: 1,0:13:50.41,0:13:52.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,毁掉我们英雄的好名声
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.41,0:13:52.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,ruining the good name of our heroes
Dialogue: 1,0:13:52.35,0:13:53.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,凡是有正义感的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.35,0:13:53.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No right-minded
Dialogue: 1,0:13:53.60,0:13:55.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,美人鱼战士和企鹅男孩社社员
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.60,0:13:55.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mermaidman and Barnacleboy society member
Dialogue: 1,0:13:55.90,0:13:57.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都不会花钱看这部
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.90,0:13:57.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,would ever pay to see this
Dialogue: 1,0:13:57.71,0:14:00.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这部烂片
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.71,0:14:00.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,this celluloid hoax
Dialogue: 1,0:14:00.25,0:14:02.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我提议抵制这部电影
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.25,0:14:02.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I say we boycott this movie
Dialogue: 1,0:14:02.77,0:14:04.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁挺我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.77,0:14:04.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now who's with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.15,0:14:05.53,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(310,246)}裤头村活动中心
Dialogue: 1,0:14:05.70,0:14:06.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,叛徒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.70,0:14:06.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Traitors
Dialogue: 1,0:14:06.65,0:14:08.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就等我们跟美人鱼战士说这件事好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.65,0:14:08.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait till we tell Mermaidman about this
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.70,0:14:10.87,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1090,606)}荫凉滩疗养院
Dialogue: 1,0:14:10.62,0:14:12.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,B47
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.62,0:14:12.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,B-47
Dialogue: 1,0:14:12.95,0:14:14.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,帮扣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.95,0:14:14.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bonko
Dialogue: 1,0:14:14.32,0:14:15.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,应该说  宾果
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.32,0:14:15.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's "Bingo"
Dialogue: 1,0:14:15.95,0:14:17.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你手别碰我  女的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.95,0:14:17.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get your hands off me, woman
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.66,0:14:21.79,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(746,224)}宾果
Dialogue: 1,0:14:17.92,0:14:19.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,A29
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.92,0:14:19.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A-29
Dialogue: 1,0:14:19.95,0:14:21.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太老了  演不了动作片
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.95,0:14:21.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Too old for an action movie
Dialogue: 1,0:14:22.42,0:14:23.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这次又怎么了  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.42,0:14:23.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What is it this time, kid?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:23.98,0:14:26.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们就不知道德瑞皮兄弟制片厂在拍
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.98,0:14:26.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you aware that Drippy Brothers Studios is making
Dialogue: 1,0:14:26.66,0:14:28.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,美人鱼战士和企鹅男孩大电影吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.66,0:14:28.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the Mermaidman and Barnacleboy movie?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:28.51,0:14:30.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他们不可能会拍我们的电影
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.51,0:14:30.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They can't be making a movie about us
Dialogue: 1,0:14:30.55,0:14:31.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可他们真拍了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.55,0:14:31.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But they are
Dialogue: 1,0:14:31.75,0:14:32.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而且还用了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.75,0:14:32.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And they're using
Dialogue: 1,0:14:32.76,0:14:33.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,演员
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.76,0:14:33.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,actors
Dialogue: 1,0:14:35.18,0:14:37.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他们有意回避了我们的英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.18,0:14:37.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They have shunned our heroes
Dialogue: 1,0:14:37.14,0:14:38.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而且也对他们不是很友善
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.14,0:14:38.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And they weren't nice to them either
Dialogue: 1,0:14:40.82,0:14:44.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这下我们登上大银幕的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.82,0:14:44.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now our dreams of being big-screen heroes
Dialogue: 1,0:14:44.37,0:14:46.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再也没法实现了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.37,0:14:46.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,will never come true
Dialogue: 1,0:14:46.28,0:14:48.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这样就更严重了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.28,0:14:48.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, that makes it even worse
Dialogue: 1,0:14:48.07,0:14:50.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最好是这样  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.07,0:14:50.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You bet it does, kid
Dialogue: 1,0:14:50.40,0:14:52.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最严重的就是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.40,0:14:52.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And the worst part is
Dialogue: 1,0:14:52.58,0:14:55.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我忘了我干嘛要哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.58,0:14:55.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't remember why I started crying
Dialogue: 1,0:14:58.16,0:15:00.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不然我们自制一部电影吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.16,0:15:00.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why don't we just make our own movie?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:00.17,0:15:03.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  你的才能又发光发热了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.17,0:15:03.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, once again you have exposed your brilliance
Dialogue: 1,0:15:03.29,0:15:04.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就拍一部真正的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.29,0:15:04.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We'll make a real
Dialogue: 1,0:15:04.37,0:15:06.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,美人鱼战士和企鹅男孩大电影
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.37,0:15:06.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mermaidman and Barnacleboy movie
Dialogue: 1,0:15:06.40,0:15:08.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就在荫凉滩这里拍
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.40,0:15:08.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Right here at Shady Shoals
Dialogue: 1,0:15:08.42,0:15:09.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.42,0:15:09.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You will?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:09.26,0:15:10.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.26,0:15:10.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 1,0:15:10.07,0:15:13.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这样就能帮你们拨乱反正
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.07,0:15:13.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And in doing so, we will right the wrong done to you
Dialogue: 1,0:15:13.31,0:15:15.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,纠正邪恶的德瑞皮兄弟制片厂和
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.31,0:15:15.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,by the evil Drippy Brothers Studios and
Dialogue: 1,0:15:16.04,0:15:17.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他们的演员
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.04,0:15:17.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,their actors
Dialogue: 1,0:15:18.50,0:15:20.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,平反是我们的责任
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.50,0:15:20.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Vindication is ours
Dialogue: 1,0:15:20.76,0:15:21.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,平
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.76,0:15:21.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Vindi
Dialogue: 1,0:15:22.35,0:15:24.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我怎么上来的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.35,0:15:24.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How did I get up here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.19,0:15:25.82,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(434,382)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:15:24.96,0:15:27.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  电影一开始需要什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.96,0:15:27.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, Patrick, what do we need to start a movie?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:27.40,0:15:28.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,爆米花吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.40,0:15:28.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Popcorn?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:28.45,0:15:29.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.45,0:15:29.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:15:29.12,0:15:30.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我问的是拍电影
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.12,0:15:30.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to start making a movie
Dialogue: 1,0:15:31.19,0:15:32.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来先定下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.19,0:15:32.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's start with
Dialogue: 1,0:15:32.95,0:15:33.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,标题
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.95,0:15:33.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the title
Dialogue: 1,0:15:33.95,0:15:34.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.95,0:15:34.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:15:36.24,0:15:36.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我想到了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.24,0:15:36.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got one
Dialogue: 1,0:15:37.31,0:15:40.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,地下城历险记
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.31,0:15:40.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Adventures in the Underground City"
Dialogue: 1,0:15:40.61,0:15:41.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,很好  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.61,0:15:41.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Great, Pat
Dialogue: 1,0:15:41.34,0:15:42.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有啥情节
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.34,0:15:42.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What happens?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:42.00,0:15:43.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有这么一座城
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.00,0:15:43.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, there's a city
Dialogue: 1,0:15:43.08,0:15:43.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,城
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.08,0:15:43.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,City
Dialogue: 1,0:15:43.75,0:15:44.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就在地下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.75,0:15:44.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and it's underground
Dialogue: 1,0:15:44.59,0:15:45.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,地下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.59,0:15:45.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Underground
Dialogue: 1,0:15:45.42,0:15:46.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,主角展开了历险记
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.42,0:15:46.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and they have an adventure
Dialogue: 1,0:15:46.55,0:15:47.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,历险记
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.55,0:15:47.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Adventure
Dialogue: 1,0:15:47.30,0:15:48.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,剧终
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.30,0:15:48.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The end
Dialogue: 1,0:15:48.09,0:15:48.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,终
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.09,0:15:48.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,End
Dialogue: 1,0:15:48.71,0:15:50.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,非常棒  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.71,0:15:50.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's great, Pat
Dialogue: 1,0:15:51.12,0:15:51.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好像有点短了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.12,0:15:51.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Seems kinda short
Dialogue: 1,0:15:51.97,0:15:53.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我有个办法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.97,0:15:53.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I have an idea
Dialogue: 1,0:15:53.25,0:15:54.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让它变长一点
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.25,0:15:54.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's make it longer
Dialogue: 1,0:15:55.00,0:15:55.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,变长  好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.00,0:15:55.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Longer, yes
Dialogue: 1,0:15:55.87,0:15:57.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那就让美人鱼战士
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.87,0:15:57.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's have Mermaidman
Dialogue: 1,0:15:57.48,0:16:00.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,脸被海草怪的脸部缩小机缩小
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.48,0:16:00.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,get his face shrunk by Kelp-Thing's face minimizer
Dialogue: 1,0:16:00.23,0:16:02.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  然后他
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.23,0:16:02.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, and then he, um
Dialogue: 1,0:16:02.83,0:16:03.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他喝了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.83,0:16:03.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,he drinks
Dialogue: 1,0:16:03.90,0:16:05.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,芝士咖啡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.90,0:16:05.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,cheese coffee
Dialogue: 1,0:16:07.19,0:16:08.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真好笑  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.19,0:16:08.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good one, Pat
Dialogue: 1,0:16:09.92,0:16:11.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们几个在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.92,0:16:11.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What are ye lads doing?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:11.23,0:16:12.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们在拍电影
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.23,0:16:12.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're making a movie
Dialogue: 1,0:16:12.53,0:16:13.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.53,0:16:13.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Great
Dialogue: 1,0:16:13.33,0:16:16.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我正好有最新兴的影星
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.33,0:16:16.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got cinema's newest star right here
Dialogue: 1,0:16:19.67,0:16:20.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你说怎么样  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.67,0:16:20.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What do you say, lad?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:20.94,0:16:22.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好啊  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.94,0:16:22.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sure, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:16:22.08,0:16:23.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珍珍可以来参演
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.08,0:16:23.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pearl can be in our movie
Dialogue: 1,0:16:23.21,0:16:24.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我说的不是珍珍
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.21,0:16:24.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I wasn't talking about Pearl
Dialogue: 1,0:16:24.72,0:16:27.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我说的是蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.72,0:16:27.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I was talking about the Krabby Patty
Dialogue: 1,0:16:29.67,0:16:30.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你也可以参演  珍珍
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.67,0:16:30.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You can be in it, too, Pearl
Dialogue: 1,0:16:31.15,0:16:33.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要变成影星了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.15,0:16:33.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm going to be a movie star
Dialogue: 1,0:16:33.68,0:16:35.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来认识一下技艺高超的专家
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.68,0:16:35.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's meet the highly skilled professionals
Dialogue: 1,0:16:35.91,0:16:37.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他们可以帮忙实现
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.91,0:16:37.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,who will help us fulfill
Dialogue: 1,0:16:37.01,0:16:39.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你登上大银幕的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.01,0:16:39.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,your dream of being on the big screen
Dialogue: 1,0:16:39.52,0:16:42.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪负责特技和爆炸场面
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.52,0:16:42.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sandy will handle the stunts and explosives
Dialogue: 1,0:16:42.00,0:16:42.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.00,0:16:42.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Howdy
Dialogue: 1,0:16:42.63,0:16:44.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珍珍是女主演
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.63,0:16:44.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pearl is the leading lady
Dialogue: 1,0:16:44.27,0:16:46.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板为摄制提供餐饮
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.27,0:16:46.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs will cater the affair
Dialogue: 1,0:16:46.42,0:16:48.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星负责摄影
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.42,0:16:48.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick will run the camera
Dialogue: 1,0:16:49.61,0:16:50.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这位是章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.61,0:16:50.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:16:50.97,0:16:52.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他负责化妆组
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.97,0:16:52.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's in charge of the makeup department
Dialogue: 1,0:16:53.28,0:16:54.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.28,0:16:54.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, thanks
Dialogue: 1,0:16:54.60,0:16:56.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁想当什么化妆组
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.60,0:16:56.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who wants to be the "makeup department"?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:56.95,0:17:01.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不是化妆组  你当的是化妆艺术家
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.95,0:17:01.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not makeup department, you're the makeup artist
Dialogue: 1,0:17:01.50,0:17:02.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,艺术家
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.50,0:17:02.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Artist?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:02.50,0:17:03.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,化妆艺术家
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.50,0:17:03.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Makeup artist
Dialogue: 1,0:17:04.20,0:17:07.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那我就来把演员化得美美的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.20,0:17:07.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,In that case, let's make those old crabapples sizzle
Dialogue: 1,0:17:10.82,0:17:13.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,艺术家要来创造美了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.82,0:17:13.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Time for the art-eest to go to work
Dialogue: 1,0:17:31.45,0:17:32.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.45,0:17:32.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Voilà
Dialogue: 1,0:17:33.12,0:17:34.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家请就位
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.12,0:17:34.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, places, everybody
Dialogue: 1,0:17:35.11,0:17:37.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  主角准备好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.11,0:17:37.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward, are our heroes ready?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:37.45,0:17:38.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好得不能再好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.45,0:17:38.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,As they'll ever be
Dialogue: 1,0:17:41.87,0:17:43.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他们好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.87,0:17:43.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They're beautiful
Dialogue: 1,0:17:43.80,0:17:45.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就跟三十年前一个样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.80,0:17:45.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They look just like they did 30 years ago
Dialogue: 1,0:17:47.50,0:17:48.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  开拍
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.50,0:17:48.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, action
Dialogue: 1,0:17:51.71,0:17:53.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我爱我的新工作
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.71,0:17:53.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I love my new job
Dialogue: 1,0:17:53.34,0:17:54.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,干得漂亮  珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.34,0:17:54.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good job, Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:17:55.97,0:17:57.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我  射线恶魔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.97,0:17:57.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I, Man Ray
Dialogue: 1,0:17:57.55,0:18:00.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,自黑暗深渊回归
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.55,0:18:00.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,have returned from the murky depths
Dialogue: 1,0:18:00.02,0:18:03.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,报仇雪恨  并将你们的灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.02,0:18:03.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to seek my revenge and banish your souls
Dialogue: 1,0:18:03.90,0:18:05.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放逐至下界
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.90,0:18:05.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to the nether regions
Dialogue: 1,0:18:05.53,0:18:07.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他们的防御力虽强
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.53,0:18:07.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Their defenses are strong
Dialogue: 1,0:18:07.57,0:18:11.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但是敌不过我的射线恶魔射线
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.57,0:18:11.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But they're no match for my Man-Ray ray
Dialogue: 1,0:18:11.40,0:18:12.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.40,0:18:12.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:12.46,0:18:15.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  这角色是为我量身打造的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.46,0:18:15.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, this role was made for me
Dialogue: 1,0:18:15.49,0:18:17.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可这电影都没射线恶魔戏份
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.49,0:18:17.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That villain isn't even in this movie
Dialogue: 1,0:18:17.32,0:18:18.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过还是先看有啥活
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.32,0:18:18.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But let me see if we have something
Dialogue: 1,0:18:18.71,0:18:20.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可以符合你的条件吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.71,0:18:20.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that fits your qualifications
Dialogue: 1,0:18:20.85,0:18:21.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来活儿了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.85,0:18:21.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here's something
Dialogue: 1,0:18:21.64,0:18:23.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你可以当杆爷来现场收音
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.64,0:18:23.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You can be the boom operator
Dialogue: 1,0:18:23.22,0:18:25.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我以为珊迪就是杆爷
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.22,0:18:25.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I thought Sandy was the boom operator
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.22,0:18:25.59,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\pos(918,920)}炸
Dialogue: 1,0:18:25.59,0:18:27.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有谁说到爆炸了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.59,0:18:27.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Did somebody say "boom"?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:28.54,0:18:30.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.54,0:18:30.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:18:30.72,0:18:32.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你这可是白瞎了我的才华
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.72,0:18:32.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But you're squandering my talents
Dialogue: 1,0:18:33.87,0:18:36.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  开始拍摄
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.87,0:18:36.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, Patrick, start the movie
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.09,0:18:38.09,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(680,550)}美人鱼战士和企鹅男孩大电影\N第一次拍摄
Dialogue: 1,0:18:37.09,0:18:38.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,第一次拍摄
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.09,0:18:38.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Take one
Dialogue: 1,0:18:38.65,0:18:42.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一定要夺回那些失节的蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.65,0:18:42.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We have to get back those swollen Krabby Patties
Dialogue: 1,0:18:42.47,0:18:43.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,停
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.47,0:18:43.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Cut
Dialogue: 1,0:18:43.23,0:18:44.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对  美人鱼战士
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.23,0:18:44.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, Mermaidman
Dialogue: 1,0:18:44.24,0:18:46.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是  失窃的蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.24,0:18:46.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,it's "stolen Krabby Patties"
Dialogue: 1,0:18:46.62,0:18:47.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,第二次拍摄
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.62,0:18:47.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Take Two
Dialogue: 1,0:18:48.18,0:18:49.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一定要夺回
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.18,0:18:49.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We have to get back
Dialogue: 1,0:18:49.25,0:18:51.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那些失窃的蟹房包去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.25,0:18:51.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to those stolen maggie daddies
Dialogue: 1,0:18:51.56,0:18:52.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,停
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.56,0:18:52.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Cut
Dialogue: 1,0:18:52.40,0:18:53.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对  美人鱼战士
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.40,0:18:53.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, Mermaidman
Dialogue: 1,0:18:53.56,0:18:55.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是  失窃的蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.56,0:18:55.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,it's "stolen Krabby Patties"
Dialogue: 1,0:18:56.02,0:18:58.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,第5003次拍摄
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.02,0:18:58.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Take 5,003
Dialogue: 1,0:18:59.02,0:19:03.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一定要夺回那些失窃的蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.02,0:19:03.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We have to get back those stolen Krabby Patties
Dialogue: 1,0:19:03.35,0:19:06.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要是不阻止那个可恶的坏蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.35,0:19:06.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And if we don't stop that diabolical scoundrel
Dialogue: 1,0:19:08.54,0:19:09.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还回来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.54,0:19:09.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Give it back
Dialogue: 1,0:19:09.40,0:19:12.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,果然是个馊主意
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.40,0:19:12.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I knew this was a bad idea
Dialogue: 1,0:19:12.04,0:19:12.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,停
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.04,0:19:12.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Cut
Dialogue: 1,0:19:12.64,0:19:13.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,痞老板  下次
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.64,0:19:13.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Plankton, next time
Dialogue: 1,0:19:13.92,0:19:15.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可不可以别让麦入镜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.92,0:19:15.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,could you keep the boom out of the shot?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:15.60,0:19:17.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,除此之外  你的工作非常出色
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.60,0:19:17.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Other than that, you're doing a super job
Dialogue: 1,0:19:17.48,0:19:19.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太丢脸了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.48,0:19:19.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is humiliating
Dialogue: 1,0:19:19.47,0:19:21.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我根本就不擅长当杆爷
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.47,0:19:21.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm not good at this boom thing
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.47,0:19:21.02,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\pos(952,920)}炸
Dialogue: 1,0:19:21.17,0:19:23.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有谁说到爆炸了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.17,0:19:23.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Did somebody say "boom"?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:25.29,0:19:26.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.29,0:19:26.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, Daddy
Dialogue: 1,0:19:26.61,0:19:29.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你说我会变明星的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.61,0:19:29.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you said I was going to be a star
Dialogue: 1,0:19:29.47,0:19:30.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错  珍珍
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.47,0:19:30.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You are, Pearl
Dialogue: 1,0:19:30.65,0:19:32.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,美人鱼战士没你  哪都去不了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.65,0:19:32.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mermaidman wouldn't get anywhere without you
Dialogue: 1,0:19:33.42,0:19:35.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快上场吧  加油
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.42,0:19:35.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Go out there and break a leg
Dialogue: 1,0:19:35.50,0:19:36.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.50,0:19:36.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:19:36.65,0:19:38.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  开拍
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.65,0:19:38.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, action
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.07,0:19:39.49,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(756,316)}海草怪藏身处
Dialogue: 1,0:19:39.85,0:19:42.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,前往无影船
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.85,0:19:42.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,To the boatmobile
Dialogue: 1,0:19:43.49,0:19:44.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,上音效
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.49,0:19:44.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Cue sound effects
Dialogue: 1,0:19:48.26,0:19:50.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,听听这发动机突的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.26,0:19:50.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Listen to that engine purr
Dialogue: 1,0:19:55.08,0:19:56.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就快到了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.08,0:19:56.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Almost there
Dialogue: 1,0:20:09.77,0:20:11.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,早安  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.77,0:20:11.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good morning, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:20:12.67,0:20:14.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,全都毁了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.67,0:20:14.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Everything's ruined
Dialogue: 1,0:20:14.62,0:20:16.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,至少拍到了画面
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.62,0:20:16.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, at least we got the footage
Dialogue: 1,0:20:16.52,0:20:18.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对  我拍到了画面
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.52,0:20:18.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I got the footage
Dialogue: 1,0:20:18.00,0:20:19.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.00,0:20:19.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, what is that?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:20.60,0:20:21.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是摄影机
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.60,0:20:21.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's a camera
Dialogue: 1,0:20:21.75,0:20:22.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.75,0:20:22.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:20:22.57,0:20:23.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这个
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.57,0:20:23.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,this
Dialogue: 1,0:20:23.49,0:20:24.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是镜头盖
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.49,0:20:24.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's a lens cap
Dialogue: 1,0:20:24.87,0:20:26.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你刚把它给盖上去了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.87,0:20:26.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Did you just put that on?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:26.42,0:20:28.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没有  我不想弄丢它
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.42,0:20:28.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, I didn't want to lose it
Dialogue: 1,0:20:28.10,0:20:30.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以拍摄前我就盖上去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.10,0:20:30.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,so I put it there right before we started filming
Dialogue: 1,0:20:44.81,0:20:46.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,电影全毁了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.81,0:20:46.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The movie's ruined
Dialogue: 1,0:20:46.70,0:20:48.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拍不了电影了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.70,0:20:48.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We can't make a movie
Dialogue: 1,0:20:48.39,0:20:49.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.39,0:20:49.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, little hero
Dialogue: 1,0:20:49.99,0:20:53.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这让我想起了第912集
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.99,0:20:53.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,this reminds me of Episode 912
Dialogue: 1,0:20:53.20,0:20:54.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们那时被包围了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.20,0:20:54.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We were surrounded
Dialogue: 1,0:20:54.65,0:20:56.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海草怪就在我们右边
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.65,0:20:56.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The Kelp-Thing was to our right
Dialogue: 1,0:20:56.52,0:20:58.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,旁边还有西兰花
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.52,0:20:58.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and there was broccoli on the side
Dialogue: 1,0:20:58.36,0:21:00.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但是假如有我唯一记得的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.36,0:21:00.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But if there's one thing I remember
Dialogue: 1,0:21:00.37,0:21:01.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那这件事就是遗忘
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.37,0:21:01.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,it's how to forget
Dialogue: 1,0:21:01.94,0:21:03.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  时机正好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.94,0:21:03.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, this is good
Dialogue: 1,0:21:03.15,0:21:03.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,开始拍摄
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.15,0:21:03.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Roll the film
Dialogue: 1,0:21:03.95,0:21:06.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,吃葡萄不吐葡萄
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.95,0:21:06.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The rain in Spain stays mainly on the
Dialogue: 1,0:21:07.10,0:21:08.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,辟
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.10,0:21:08.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Space
Dialogue: 1,0:21:08.85,0:21:10.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最后倒计时
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.85,0:21:10.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The final countdown
Dialogue: 1,0:21:10.70,0:21:11.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要坚持那个
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.70,0:21:11.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stick to the
Dialogue: 1,0:21:11.87,0:21:12.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,坚持那个
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.87,0:21:12.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,stick to the
Dialogue: 1,0:21:12.87,0:21:14.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我亲爱的卢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.87,0:21:14.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Lou, my darling
Dialogue: 1,0:21:14.62,0:21:15.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,卢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.62,0:21:15.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Lou
Dialogue: 1,0:21:16.47,0:21:19.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快去把电影拍完  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.47,0:21:19.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now get out there and finish this movie, kid
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.80,0:21:21.42,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(774,602)}电影首映
Dialogue: 1,0:21:22.76,0:21:24.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板  你哭什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.76,0:21:24.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs, why are you weeping?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:25.20,0:21:27.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我特地提早打烊来放你的电影
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.20,0:21:27.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I closed early for your movie
Dialogue: 1,0:21:27.97,0:21:29.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,花钱的客人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.97,0:21:29.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where are the paying customers?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:29.83,0:21:31.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你说好会座无虚席的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.83,0:21:31.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You promised a full house
Dialogue: 1,0:21:31.85,0:21:33.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,客人来就座了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.85,0:21:33.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And here comes the filling
Dialogue: 1,0:21:33.85,0:21:36.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,美人鱼战士和企鹅男孩粉丝俱乐部
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.85,0:21:36.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The Mermaidman and Barnacleboy Fan Club
Dialogue: 1,0:21:37.22,0:21:38.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就知道你们会来看
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.22,0:21:38.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I knew you'd come see
Dialogue: 1,0:21:38.48,0:21:40.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真正的美人鱼战士和企鹅男孩大电影
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.48,0:21:40.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the real Mermaidman and Barnacleboy movie
Dialogue: 1,0:21:40.70,0:21:42.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,其实真电影的票卖完了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.70,0:21:42.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Actually, the real movie was sold out
Dialogue: 1,0:21:42.69,0:21:44.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要买两百张票
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.69,0:21:44.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll take 200 tickets, please
Dialogue: 1,0:21:44.70,0:21:46.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这才叫美好结局嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.70,0:21:46.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, this is what I call a happy ending
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.66,0:21:47.78,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1152,566)}真\N美人鱼战士\N和企鹅男孩\N大电影
Dialogue: 1,0:21:49.42,0:21:53.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,重要时刻到来了  我们登上大银幕了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.42,0:21:53.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, our big moment, us up on the big screen
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.58,0:21:58.50,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,450)}罗克斯
Dialogue: 1,0:21:54.60,0:21:55.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,罗克斯堡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.60,0:21:55.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fort Lox
Dialogue: 1,0:21:55.82,0:21:58.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,五十多亿蟹黄堡的家
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.82,0:21:58.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,home to over five billion Krabby Patties
Dialogue: 1,0:21:58.76,0:22:03.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么样的邪恶天才敢潜入这铜墙铁壁
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.76,0:22:00.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What evil mastermind
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.42,0:22:03.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,would dare infiltrate this fortified fort
Dialogue: 1,0:22:03.28,0:22:05.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拐走里面的财宝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.28,0:22:05.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and make off with its treasure?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:05.05,0:22:06.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.05,0:22:06.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It is I
Dialogue: 1,0:22:06.24,0:22:07.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海草怪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.24,0:22:07.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Kelp-Thing
Dialogue: 1,0:22:07.15,0:22:08.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,非干不可
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.15,0:22:08.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do what I do
Dialogue: 1,0:22:08.67,0:22:09.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.67,0:22:09.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stop
Dialogue: 1,0:22:09.30,0:22:10.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你不能那样
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.30,0:22:10.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You can't do that
Dialogue: 1,0:22:10.53,0:22:11.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,禁止了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.53,0:22:11.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Forbidden
Dialogue: 1,0:22:11.70,0:22:12.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.70,0:22:12.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Watch me
Dialogue: 1,0:22:12.69,0:22:15.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,准备好感受我的怒火吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.69,0:22:15.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Prepare to feel my wrath
Dialogue: 1,0:22:15.43,0:22:16.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你这恶棍
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.43,0:22:16.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you foul villain
Dialogue: 1,0:22:22.65,0:22:25.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,虽然你可能还是成功偷到了蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.65,0:22:25.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You may have won the Krabby Patties
Dialogue: 1,0:22:25.03,0:22:26.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但是战斗仍要继续
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.03,0:22:26.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but the battle rages on
Dialogue: 1,0:22:28.91,0:22:29.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,美人鱼战士
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.91,0:22:29.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mermaidman
Dialogue: 1,0:22:30.12,0:22:31.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,鹅男孩
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.12,0:22:31.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,nacleboy
Dialogue: 1,0:22:31.55,0:22:32.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,合为一体
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.55,0:22:32.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,unite
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.37,0:22:33.66,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(736,886)}剧终
Dialogue: 1,0:22:36.00,0:22:38.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小子  你向全世界证明了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.00,0:22:38.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, kid, you showed the world
Dialogue: 1,0:22:38.27,0:22:41.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,虽然我们的步伐慢了下来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.27,0:22:41.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that even though our steps may have been slowed
Dialogue: 1,0:22:41.60,0:22:47.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但我们这把英雄老骨头还是能打的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.60,0:22:43.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,we still have a little action left
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.96,0:22:47.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,in these heroic old bones
Dialogue: 1,0:22:47.96,0:22:49.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,至少能打一点点
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.96,0:22:49.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, at least some of them
